---
layout: pages
title: Latest storms
description: Long Mastodon posts and self-reply threads exported from the local cache.
nav:
  order: 1
  title: Home
---
<section class="site-intro">
  <p>{{ site.description }}</p>
  <p>{{ storms.storm_count }} exported posts across {{ storms.authors.length }} identities. Long single posts use a {{ storms.min_text_length }} character threshold after stripping HTML, links, mentions, and hashtags.</p>
</section>

{% if storms.storms.length %}
<section class="storm-list">
  {% for storm in storms.storms %}
  <article class="storm-card">
    <header>
      <h2><a href="{{ ('/posts/' + storm.slug + '/') | relativeUrl(page.url) }}">{{ storm.title }}</a></h2>
      <div class="storm-meta">
        <span>@{{ storm.author.acct }}</span>
        <time datetime="{{ storm.created_at }}">{{ storm.created_at | formatDate }}</time>
        <span>{{ storm.cleaned_length }} cleaned characters</span>
        {% if storm.reply_count %}
        <span>{{ storm.reply_count }} self-replies</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </header>
    <p class="storm-excerpt">{{ storm.excerpt }}</p>
    <p><a href="{{ ('/posts/' + storm.slug + '/') | relativeUrl(page.url) }}">Read the thread</a></p>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
{% else %}
<p class="empty-state">No storms matched the export rules yet.</p>
{% endif %}
